</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uxaeryaare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xaer YaAre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(8/2/01 10:53:12 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/XaerYaare/GROEN.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spirit of cheetah</span><hr size=1> In any outdoor zone, cheetah/gate it is a far superior escape strategy than to just gate, especially with summoning mobs.<br>
<br>
Specialized travel situations fit:<br>
WC to EC is 1 duration of cheetah<br>
NK to SK is 1 duration of cheetah<br>
there are more.<br>
<br>
If you can prep your spells during downtime before the travel is required (common when doing ports for people), then toss on a cheeta till it refreshes, burn it, and have fun!<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uscirocco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Scirocco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>FAQ/Index Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(8/3/01 1:45:44 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Spirit of cheetah</span><hr size=1> I haven't used it since the nerf, when I used it for high speed traveling.  Gate, egress, or jboots get me out of anything that SoC could. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showMessage?topicID=2542.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showMessage?topicID=2540.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.emailToFriend?topicID=2527.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.threadControl?topicID=2527.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2527.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2527.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><